cbf.model.TestCase

  • Packages that use TestCase 
    Package Description
    cbf.engine
    Classes to run component based test cases, to track the runtime status of execution, and to encapsulate runtime exception handling, test failures and recovery.
    cbf.model
    Provides all the core interfaces related to framework.
    cbfx.factory.test
    Classes to manage testsets and testcases from different sources ALM,Designer, Json, Excel, Xml and to take care of deserializing test case after resolving the test case and data mapping for execution.
